# Cursor AI Rules for this project

## Language Requirements
- All code comments, documentation, commit messages, README files, and any other text content in this project MUST be written in simple English
- No non-English languages should be used
- Use clear, concise English that is easy to understand for international developers
- Variable names, function names, and identifiers should follow English naming conventions

## Code Style
- Follow standard conventions for the respective programming languages used in this project
- Write descriptive comments explaining complex logic
- Use meaningful variable and function names in English
- Keep documentation clear and accessible to English speakers

## Documentation
- All README files, configuration guides, and project documentation must be in English
- Use simple, straightforward language to explain concepts
- Avoid complex technical jargon when simpler terms suffice
- Examples and code snippets should include English comments where appropriate
